628
00:53:28.623 --> 00:53:30.723
<i>The Archbishop of Ethiopia.</i>

629
00:53:35.223 --> 00:53:36.623
<i>You need to find the shooter.</i>

630
00:53:40.023 --> 00:53:41.023
No.

631
00:55:34.329 --> 00:55:36.829
