00:56:23.132 --> 00:56:24.532
Name was Sam.

646
00:56:25.632 --> 00:56:28.032
He was a good dog.
I raised him from a pup.

647
00:56:32.232 --> 00:56:33.333
You okay?

648
00:56:35.333 --> 00:56:36.333
No.

649
00:56:37.533 --> 00:56:39.133
What are you gonna do?

650
00:56:40.733 --> 00:56:42.333
I'll get better.

651
00:56:44.233 --> 00:56:46.633
Then I'm going to burn
their playhouse down.

652
00:57:22.635 --> 00:57:23.735
Can I help you?

653
00:57:52.737 --> 00:57:53.737
Hold still.

654
00:58:05.438 --> 00:58:07.238
I been meaning to ask you.

