00:59:32.742 --> 00:59:34.042
Excuse me?

678
00:59:35.242 --> 00:59:38.243
May be a way to get two birds
with that stone, too.

679
00:59:46.943 --> 00:59:48.743
-Swagger?
-Hey.

680
00:59:58.544 --> 01:00:01.144
The gun Donnie learned to hunt with
when he was a kid.

681
01:00:03.044 --> 01:00:06.344
It ain't much, but it shoots true.

682
01:00:06.644 --> 01:00:08.944
