688
01:00:26.045 --> 01:00:28.221
I'm still enough of a sucker,
you press that patriot button,

689
01:00:28.245 --> 01:00:31.645
I'll sit up in my chair and say,
"Which way you want me to go, boss?"

690
01:00:31.945 --> 01:00:35.346
I mean, I ain't real proud of it,
but I ain't ashamed, either.

691
01:00:36.946 --> 01:00:38.246
You know, I got a plan,

692
01:00:39.646 --> 01:00:41.846
but I think I'm going to need your help.

693
01:00:42.146 --> 01:00:43.946
Okay. I'll do it.

694
01:00:44.746 --> 01:00:46.946
I haven't even told you what it is yet.

695
01:00:47.746 --> 01:00:48.746
I know.

696
01:00:56.647 --> 01:00:57.747
Look.

697
01:00:58.847 --> 01:01:00.147
It was my fault.

698
01:01:02.947 --> 01:01:03.947
What?

