01:02:22.251 --> 01:02:23.452
It's okay.

712
01:02:29.452 --> 01:02:31.652
<i>I need you to meet with this FBI agent.</i>

713
01:02:31.852 --> 01:02:34.452
<i>Use him to flush Johnson
